scripts.post-update: echo "codesandbox preview only, need an update" && yarn upgrade --latest
scripts.generate: rm -rf node_modules/.cache && next build && next export
scripts.deploy: touch out/.nojekyll && git add -f out && git commit -m "Deploy Next.js to gh-pages" && git subtree push --prefix out origin gh-pages
scripts.deploy-win: git add -f out && git commit -m "Deploy Next.js to gh-pages" && git subtree push --prefix out origin gh-pages
